Class BaseReport<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.internal.reports.excelreport.BaseReport<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DetailsReport, SummaryReport, TestOutputReport

    public abstract class BaseReport<T>
extends Object
    Parent class to support all Reports. The data that it contains has to be specified as T. Right now works with SummarizedData and List of Strings as Data
